---
title: Takeaway Style Prawn Fried Rice with Bell Pepper, Peas and Fried Egg
description: Inspired by a popular takeaway favourite, top this dish with a fried egg for extra deliciousness! Layers of flavour with spring onion, fragrant lemongrass and sambal make this easy Chinese style dish full of flavour.
HIGH PROTEIN - Protein contributes to the maintenance of muscle mass.
